/**
 * File: cojo_texture.h
 * Description: Rotozoom texture + 16-colour palette for cojorotozoom.
 *
 * Source: top image of atarist-silly-demo/resources/C23CUT.PNG,
 * 256x64 strip, re-indexed by LUMINANCE into 5 logo shades
 * (idx 1=darkest .. 5=brightest); image black -> idx 15
 * (TRANSPARENT so the girder grid shows through).
 *
 * Palette is fully allocated: idx 0 = white (HUD), 1..5 = logo
 * metallic-blue ramp, 6..10 = scroller pink ramp (shared with the
 * FONT.PNG scroller in cojo_font.h), 11..14 = grid greys,
 * 15 = black. Texture auto-generated; palette hand-tuned.
 */

